headline: Just two U.S. makers of critical railroad material left after plant closure
summary: Cleveland-Cliffs will close its idle Steelton, Pa., facility permanently, leaving just two U.S. producers of steel rail for track. The post Just two U.S. makers of critical railroad material left after plant closure appeared first on FreightWaves.
